OL,3,C'We try to be vigilant': businesses
OL,4,Cand police reflect on shoplifting
OL,6,FShoplifting is on the rise in Cumbria,
OL,7,Fwith police figures showing a 1.8%
OL,8,Fincrease in offences over the past
OL,9,Fyear.
OL,11,FIn the 12 months up to November 2025,
OL,12,F2,485 shoplifting incidents were
OL,13,Freported to Cumbria Constabulary, with
OL,14,FCarlisle suffering the highest rate of
OL,15,Ftheft.
OL,17,FPolice say that the Constabulary is
OL,18,Ftargeting shoplifting with visible
OL,19,Fpatrols, and that it wants retailers
OL,20,Fto know the force takes the crime
OL,21,Fseriously.
