OL,3,C'We try to be vigilant': businesses
OL,4,Cand police reflect on shoplifting
OL,6,FInspector Andy Leather told ITV
OL,7,FBorder: "Within Carlisle one of the
OL,8,Fhotspots is within the city centre,
OL,9,Fwithin the shopping area. This
OL,10,Fparticular area has benefited from
OL,11,Fadditional high visibility patrols.
OL,13,F"We're working with local businesses,
OL,14,Fpartner agencies, but also working
OL,15,Fwith retailers and instilling that
OL,16,Fconfidence within them that they
OL,17,Fshould report (shoplifting) to Cumbria
OL,18,FPolice.
