OL,3,C'We try to be vigilant': businesses
OL,4,Cand police reflect on shoplifting
OL,6,F"They should have confidence that if
OL,7,Fthey do report to Cumbria Police we
OL,8,Fwill investigate it, we will take it
OL,9,Fseriously, and when appropriate we
OL,10,Fwill look to prosecute."
OL,12,FOne Cumbrian business which has
OL,13,Finvested in technology to deter and
OL,14,Fdetect shoplifters is Cranstons.
