OL,3,C'We try to be vigilant': businesses
OL,4,Cand police reflect on shoplifting
OL,6,FPeter Potts, head of retail at
OL,7,FCranstons said: "We've upgraded CCTV
OL,8,Fsystems, upgraded cameras so it's
OL,9,Fclearer and better evidence.
OL,10,FInternally, staff are given a what to
OL,11,Fdo guide, we try to be vigilant,
OL,12,Fdiscourage the use of things like bags
OL,13,Ffor life and have people use our
OL,14,Fbaskets.
OL,16,F"Now we have larger food halls it
OL,17,Fbecomes a little easier to attempt
OL,18,Fshoplifting, but we've also got a
OL,19,Flittle bit smarter."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
