OL,3,C'We try to be vigilant': businesses
OL,4,Cand police reflect on shoplifting
OL,6,FMr Potts says that Cranstons has not
OL,7,Fseen a huge volume of shoplifting
OL,8,Foffences: "We don't suffer from it too
OL,9,Fmuch, (but) we are a store with a lot
OL,10,Fof staff which helps us quite a bit.
OL,12,F"I've worked for Cranstons for 32
OL,13,Fyears. In more recent times we've
OL,14,Fnoticed people trying to steal larger
OL,15,Fitems... in years gone past it was
OL,16,Fstealing to feed yourself, or alcohol,
OL,17,Fnow we're seeing a trend of people
OL,18,Ftrying to steal larger bulk packs."
