OL,3,C'We try to be vigilant': businesses
OL,4,Cand police reflect on shoplifting
OL,6,FEven if there are businesses affected
OL,7,Fmore by shoplifting, Mr Potts points
OL,8,Fout that its effect on the business'
OL,9,Fbottom line is palpable, and that it
OL,10,Fcould affect the viability of jobs.
OL,12,FHe said: "It's hard to make a living
OL,13,Fthese days. We employ a lot of people,
OL,14,Fwe are very aware that we are
OL,15,Fresponsible for a lot of people's
OL,16,Flivelihoods, and this is making it
OL,17,Fharder for us.
OL,19,F"This is why we put a lot of work into
OL,20,Ftrying to stop it."
